    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b].[Id], [b].[BeyannameTipiId], [b].[Donem], [b].[Durum], [b].[GondermeTarihi], [b].[MukellefId], [b].[SonGondermeTarihi], [b].[Yil]
    FROM [dbo].[Beyanname] AS [b]
    ORDER BY [b].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[Mukellef] AS [m] ON [t].[MukellefId] = [m].[Id]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[BeyannameTipi] AS [b0] ON [t].[BeyannameTipiId] = [b0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC

22.12.2025 03:01:34 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [m].[Ad], [b0].[Ad], [t].[Yil], COALESCE([t].[Donem], N''), COALESCE([t].[Durum], N''), CASE
    WHEN [t].[SonGondermeTarihi] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[SonGondermeTarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b].[Id], [b].[BeyannameTipiId], [b].[Donem], [b].[Durum], [b].[MukellefId], [b].[SonGondermeTarihi], [b].[Yil]
    FROM [dbo].[Beyanname] AS [b]
    ORDER BY [b].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[Mukellef] AS [m] ON [t].[MukellefId] = [m].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [m].[Ad], [b0].[Ad], [t].[Yil], COALESCE([t].[Donem], N''), COALESCE([t].[Durum], N''), CASE
    WHEN [t].[SonGondermeTarihi] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[SonGondermeTarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b].[Id], [b].[BeyannameTipiId], [b].[Donem], [b].[Durum], [b].[MukellefId], [b].[SonGondermeTarihi], [b].[Yil]
    FROM [dbo].[Beyanname] AS [b]
    ORDER BY [b].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[Mukellef] AS [m] ON [t].[MukellefId] = [m].[Id]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[BeyannameTipi] AS [b0] ON [t].[BeyannameTipiId] = [b0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC

    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[SonGondermeTarihi]
FROM (

) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [dbo].[Mukellef] AS [m] ON [t].[MukellefId] = [m].[Id]

    WHEN [t].[SonGondermeTarihi] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[SonGondermeTarihi]

END, [t].[SonGondermeTarihi]
